{"title":"Projects","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"Projects","page-layout":"full","toc":false,"listing":{"id":"project-listing","contents":"projects.yml","type":"grid","fields":["image","title","description","categories","date"],"sort":"date desc","grid-columns":2,"image-height":"180px"}},"containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n```{=html}\n<section style=\"padding: 4rem 0 2rem;\">\n  <div class=\"section-label\">Portfolio</div>\n  <h1>Projects</h1>\n  <hr class=\"neon-rule\">\n  <p style=\"max-width:55ch; font-size:1.05rem;\">\n    A collection of analytical and technical projects built across my degree.\n    Each one started with a question — the code came after.\n  </p>\n</section>\n```\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"card-grid\" style=\"padding-bottom: 5rem;\">\n\n  <a href=\"data-analysis.qmd\" class=\"project-card\">\n    <div class=\"card-tag\">Data Analysis · Python</div>\n    <h3>Exploratory Sales Analysis</h3>\n    <p>\n      Cleaned and explored a retail sales dataset using Pandas. Found seasonal\n      patterns and top-performing SKUs through visual EDA and grouped aggregations.\n    </p>\n    <div class=\"pill-group\">\n      <span class=\"pill pill-neon\">Python</span>\n      <span class=\"pill\">Pandas</span>\n      <span class=\"pill\">Plotly</span>\n      <span class=\"pill\">EDA</span>\n    </div>\n  </a>\n\n  <a href=\"machine-learning.qmd\" class=\"project-card\">\n    <div class=\"card-tag\">Machine Learning</div>\n    <h3>Customer Churn Predictor</h3>\n    <p>\n      Trained a Random Forest classifier on a telecom dataset to predict churn.\n      Explored feature importance and evaluated performance with a confusion matrix.\n    </p>\n    <div class=\"pill-group\">\n      <span class=\"pill pill-neon\">Scikit-learn</span>\n      <span class=\"pill\">Pandas</span>\n      <span class=\"pill\">Random Forest</span>\n    </div>\n  </a>\n\n  <a href=\"dashboard.qmd\" class=\"project-card\">\n    <div class=\"card-tag\">Dashboard · Visualisation</div>\n    <h3>Interactive KPI Dashboard</h3>\n    <p>\n      Built an interactive multi-panel dashboard with Plotly Express to track\n      business KPIs — revenue, churn, and acquisition costs — with live filtering.\n    </p>\n    <div class=\"pill-group\">\n      <span class=\"pill pill-neon\">Plotly</span>\n      <span class=\"pill\">Python</span>\n      <span class=\"pill\">BI</span>\n    </div>\n  </a>\n\n  <a href=\"business-strategy.qmd\" class=\"project-card\">\n    <div class=\"card-tag\">Business Strategy</div>\n    <h3>Market Entry Analysis</h3>\n    <p>\n      Data-driven market entry analysis for a hypothetical SaaS product.\n      Combines Porter's Five Forces with publicly available market size data.\n    </p>\n    <div class=\"pill-group\">\n      <span class=\"pill\">Strategy</span>\n      <span class=\"pill\">Research</span>\n      <span class=\"pill\">Frameworks</span>\n    </div>\n  </a>\n\n</div>\n```\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n```{=html}\n<section style=\"padding: 4rem 0 2rem;\">\n  <div class=\"section-label\">Portfolio</div>\n  <h1>Projects</h1>\n  <hr class=\"neon-rule\">\n  <p style=\"max-width:55ch; font-size:1.05rem;\">\n    A collection of analytical and technical projects built across my degree.\n    Each one started with a question — the code came after.\n  </p>\n</section>\n```\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"card-grid\" style=\"padding-bottom: 5rem;\">\n\n  <a href=\"data-analysis.qmd\" class=\"project-card\">\n    <div class=\"card-tag\">Data Analysis · Python</div>\n    <h3>Exploratory Sales Analysis</h3>\n    <p>\n      Cleaned and explored a retail sales dataset using Pandas. Found seasonal\n      patterns and top-performing SKUs through visual EDA and grouped aggregations.\n    </p>\n    <div class=\"pill-group\">\n      <span class=\"pill pill-neon\">Python</span>\n      <span class=\"pill\">Pandas</span>\n      <span class=\"pill\">Plotly</span>\n      <span class=\"pill\">EDA</span>\n    </div>\n  </a>\n\n  <a href=\"machine-learning.qmd\" cl